  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Bazaar Simulator\" is a detailed first-person simulation that allows you to experience the bustling life of a traditional fruit and vegetable market. Start your journey with a lemon stand and take steps towards building your own market empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collaboration with Multiplayer Feature</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collaborate online with friends or other players. Manage larger markets together, share resources, and support each other on the path to becoming the best market vendor. Enjoy a realistic market experience together.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/6341f4d7aa682f1da525fa68ba99516d.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/6341f4d7aa682f1da525fa68ba99516d.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/6341f4d7aa682f1da525fa68ba99516d.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Traditional and Digital Scale Systems</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accurately weigh your fruits and vegetables using the traditional scale system used in markets. As you grow your business, upgrade to digital scales to increase speed and efficiency. Enhance your scale systems to provide the best service to your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/7da92dcd17b721c45362a94e73b22ecd.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/7da92dcd17b721c45362a94e73b22ecd.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/7da92dcd17b721c45362a94e73b22ecd.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stock Ordering and Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully purchase, organize, and transfer your stock from crates to stalls. Remember, fruits and vegetables spoil over time; effective stock management is critical to your success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/212032fe8f655f60e2c2169c0976418d.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/212032fe8f655f60e2c2169c0976418d.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/212032fe8f655f60e2c2169c0976418d.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fishing and Product Variety</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your product variety by adding fresh fish to your market stall. Offer a wider selection to your customers by fishing or sourcing fish, and become the most preferred stall in the market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/27e0a79656dda0c4b943735586514006.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/27e0a79656dda0c4b943735586514006.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/27e0a79656dda0c4b943735586514006.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interactive Sales Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist customers in their choices and manage payments both in cash and via QR code or IBAN. Ensure every customer leaves satisfied, creating repeat customers and a lively market atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/544ecaa1458e50ab65f049cd2d50fe16.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/544ecaa1458e50ab65f049cd2d50fe16.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/544ecaa1458e50ab65f049cd2d50fe16.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adapt to Market Fluctuations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase products when prices are low in a dynamic market environment and set competitive sales prices. Grow your business by balancing profit margins with customer satisfaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>From Lemon Stand to Market Empire</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every choice in \"Bazaar Simulator\" affects your success. Will you build your own market empire starting from a lemon stand, or will you remain a lemon vendor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >\"Bazaar Simulator\" is a detailed first-person simulation that allows you to experience the bustling life of a traditional fruit and vegetable market. Start your journey with a lemon stand and take steps towards building your own market empire.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Collaboration with Multiplayer Feature</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collaborate online with friends or other players. Manage larger markets together, share resources, and support each other on the path to becoming the best market vendor. Enjoy a realistic market experience together.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/6341f4d7aa682f1da525fa68ba99516d.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/6341f4d7aa682f1da525fa68ba99516d.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/6341f4d7aa682f1da525fa68ba99516d.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Traditional and Digital Scale Systems</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Accurately weigh your fruits and vegetables using the traditional scale system used in markets. As you grow your business, upgrade to digital scales to increase speed and efficiency. Enhance your scale systems to provide the best service to your customers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/7da92dcd17b721c45362a94e73b22ecd.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/7da92dcd17b721c45362a94e73b22ecd.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/7da92dcd17b721c45362a94e73b22ecd.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Stock Ordering and Management</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Carefully purchase, organize, and transfer your stock from crates to stalls. Remember, fruits and vegetables spoil over time; effective stock management is critical to your success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/212032fe8f655f60e2c2169c0976418d.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/212032fe8f655f60e2c2169c0976418d.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/212032fe8f655f60e2c2169c0976418d.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Fishing and Product Variety</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Increase your product variety by adding fresh fish to your market stall. Offer a wider selection to your customers by fishing or sourcing fish, and become the most preferred stall in the market.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/27e0a79656dda0c4b943735586514006.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/27e0a79656dda0c4b943735586514006.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/27e0a79656dda0c4b943735586514006.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Interactive Sales Experience</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assist customers in their choices and manage payments both in cash and via QR code or IBAN. Ensure every customer leaves satisfied, creating repeat customers and a lively market atmosphere.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/544ecaa1458e50ab65f049cd2d50fe16.poster.avif?t=1771773988\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/544ecaa1458e50ab65f049cd2d50fe16.webm?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2379810/extras/544ecaa1458e50ab65f049cd2d50fe16.mp4?t=1771773988\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Adapt to Market Fluctuations</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Purchase products when prices are low in a dynamic market environment and set competitive sales prices. Grow your business by balancing profit margins with customer satisfaction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>From Lemon Stand to Market Empire</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every choice in \"Bazaar Simulator\" affects your success. Will you build your own market empire starting from a lemon stand, or will you remain a lemon vendor</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
